{"word":"G3877 - παρακολουθέω - parakolouthéō - par-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o - Attain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρακολουθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parakolouthéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Attain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசாரித்தறி, நட, அறிந்திரு, அநுசரி"},{"paragraph":"to follow after"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G190 - ἀκολουθέω - akolouthéō - ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/190\">G190</a>; to <i>follow near</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>attend</i> (as a result), <i>trace out</i>, <i>conform</i> to: - attain, follow, fully know, have understanding.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1811/1811\">G1811</a>, <a href=\"#/G1872/1872\">G1872</a>, <a href=\"#/G190/190\">G190</a>, <a href=\"#/G3877/3877\">G3877</a>, <a href=\"#/G4870/4870\">G4870</a>"}]}